members.name: Gura
dodgequote: Woah!
healquote: Do you know what you do in this predicament, when life hui-tcha's you? You go AGAIN!
killquote: Now that's what I'm talkin' about.
deathquote: Sometimes in life, you try to hit life with a 'hui-tcha', but then life decides to hit you with a 'hui-tcha.

bio.info: A friendly and mischievous shark, Gawr Gura often plays around with her chumbuds and fellow team members. Best compared to a friend that exchanges back and forth teasing and encouragement. Despite being an over 9000 year old shark, she cleverly uses jokes and simple humor as she hangs out with friends.
bio.backstory:
A descendant of the Lost City of Atlantis, who swam to Earth while saying, ''It's so boring down there LOLOLOL!''
She bought her clothes (and her shark hat) in the human world and she really loves them. In her spare time, she enjoys talking to marine life.

bio.info: A cheerful Tanuki and somewhat egotistical, and has perfectionist tendencies. He wears a slightly loose, blue short-sleeved turtleneck to match his Brown fur with dark tan cargo shorts. And a utility belt where he keeps his shortsword around his waist. He may resemble Spectra in many ways, both being Tanukis, but Sky's tail is slightly larger, as well as being a bit fluffier. He seems to have an empty look in his eyes, though it's hard to discern.
bio.backstory: As a traveling warrior, he's seen many places and people. Through these travels, he has gained battle experience by simply mimicking what others do. Sometimes you can spot him with a leaf on his head. Being a Tanuki, he gets rather lonely, as there is almost no fellow Tanuki in the world. Spectra is the only exception to this, but as she came from a different planet, it's a bit awkward for him to approach her.
bio.theme: [Lost - Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War](https://youtu.be/dbWdn7rrxAI)
bio.likes: Flashy Moves, Evasion, Mimicking Others, Nature
bio.disikes: The Heat, Making mistakes, Discrepancies, Artificial Life

members.name: SAUM-052

magquote: [Their robotic pupils turn into a shining azure]

resistquote: ...You won't stop me with just this.
repelquote: Attack confirmed to have been bounced back... Analyzing potential cause....
drainquote: Enemy attack... Intercepted? System recovery confirmed, I will analyze this later....
hurtquote: Damage sustained. Amount recorded as... Irrelevant.
helpedquote: [Her eyes turned into the color of Sky's fur] Don't neglect your own wellbeing either.
deathquote: Damage exceeds... Operating power.... I have failed.....
lbquote: Conditions met, commencing final strike. [Their robotic pupils turn into a crimson red and show a look of cold mercilessnes]
lvlquote: Systems nominal, combat prowess increased. Results are... satisfactory.

bio.info: Her name actually has a double meaning; it also stands for 'Specialized Augmentation Unique Model 052'. While the name itself is different, the meaning is technically the same.
bio.backstory: SAUM-052, is a serial number branded by her creators. It stands for 'Special Army Unit Model 052'. She is a cold calculated killer that has previously been used in [REDACTED], now reduced to a deactivated mech in a non-disclosed [REDACTED], awaiting her inevitable re-activation, **by friend or by foe**.
bio.theme: [Alone - Call of Duty: Black Ops Cold War](https://youtu.be/5BX4FWTbTbI)

bio.info: This Tanuki is a branching off version of the original Sky. While they still share the same core values and morals, they follow different ideologies. This version is also a bit more on the fluffy side, nevertheless sharing the same appearance (except the staff on his back).
